                                     \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/digmypics-scanning-service.JPG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/digmypics-scanning-service.JPG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/digmypics-scanning-service.JPG?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/digmypics-scanning-service.JPG?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1333\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"DigMyPics scanning service\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/digmypics-scanning-service.JPG\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/digmypics-scanning-service.JPG\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"3-scan-my-photos\"\u003e\n            3.\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.scanmyphotos.com/\"\u003eScan My Photos\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCost per photo:\u003c/strong\u003e The pay-per-photo price starts at 13 cents per scan, with a $25 minimum, depending on what resolution you want. Additional services (image rotation, color correction, and same-day scanning, among others) cost extra.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFormats Supported:\u003c/strong\u003e Printed photos, film, negatives.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdditional Services:\u003c/strong\u003e Gives you the option to pay from $240 (depending on resolution) for a prepaid photo scanning box, international shipping, and rush services. These allow up to 1800 photos, so work out as a cheaper option if you\u0026#39;ve got a lot of pictures to scan.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1023\" height=\"453\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Scan My Photos is the best way to digitize old photos\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/scan-photos-to-digital.PNG\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"local-options\"\u003e\n            4. Local Options\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen choosing a service to scan your photos for you, don\u0026#39;t forget about your local photography studio or even your friendly neighborhood Walmart or Walgreens. While not all locations offer this service, this option may be more convenient and timely, if not more expensive. This can also be a better choice if you only want a few high-quality scans.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eNo matter how you digitize photos, it will lead to more space in your home, memories that are safe from harm, and a sense of gratitude that only a long trip down memory lane will afford you. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
